 BY NGOZI OKORIE UNKNOWN gunmen, on Thursday, killed a man, his wife and their daughter in Azia, Ihiala Local Government Area of Anambra State. The man, identified as Ken Ekwesianya, was reportedly killed, along with his family members, inside a church. Circumstances surrounding the killing of the deceased had not been unravelled as of the time of filing this report. Police Public Relations Officer in the state, Haruna Mohammed, confirmed the report, saying the Command was making efforts to apprehend the perpetrators of the crime and make them face the full wrath of the law. 